Load standardFirmata.pde on to Arduino Board - This can be found in Examples in the Arduino program.

This program has a button attached to digital input 2,3 and 4 on the arduino.

Check serproxy is configured to to the correct com port.  - use /dev/cu- instead of /deb/tty-

http://code.google.com/p/tinkerit/wiki/TinkerProxy

to connect to pachube - open talktophp.as change URLRequest to match where flash2pachube.php is located. - It needs to be on a server - can be hosted locally or externally.